The evidence with the title 'The gender pay gap - men, women and work ' says Oct 7, 2017  ... Women still earn a lot less than men, despite decades of equal-pay laws.  ... This is not, as many assume, because employers pay a woman less  ... Show that women earn 98% as much as men who do the same job for the same employer.  ... Likely to be male, even when most of their underlings are female. 
